OL,4,CHeatwave risk from plans to convert
OL,5,Cshops to homes
OL,6, Planning reforms to convert shops and
OL,7, restaurants into homes could lead to
OL,8, more people suffering from potentially
OL,9, deadly heatwaves, claims a report.
OL,11,FFrom 1 August, firms will be allowed to
OL,12,Fredevelop a wider range of commercial
OL,13,Fproperty into flats.
OL,15,FIt is hoped the move will regenerate
OL,16,FCity centres that have struggled during
OL,17,Fthe pandemic.
OL,19,FBut Zurich UK warns it risks creating
OL,20,Fmore poor quality homes vulnerable to
OL,21,Foverheating in the summer.
